cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.IR 

This paper deals with image recognition and machine learning, which are typically covered by the computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The paper also discusses the need for dynamic scenarios and continuous updates, which falls under the artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-category. Additionally, the use of large-scale datasets and the focus on image recognition suggest that the paper could also be classified under multimedia (cs.MM) and information retrieval (cs.IR) sub-categories.
